name: FryingSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open frying sounds”
”Alexa ask frying sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: frying sounds
des: Tssss! Let the sizzling sounds of a deep fryer help you relax to the fullest. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Frying Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
